Name: DarkLight
About the game: Darklight is a small secret room escape decryption game You need to play the role of an unknown woman who discovers the crimes of a mysterious organization in the dark basement In the game, you will be trapped in the basement. Your goal is to find a 4-digit code to escape the crime scene successfully At the same time, in this basement, you may encounter unknown monsters, and some unknown photos Naked women, bundles, guns, mechanisms and so on The game is absolutely silent, in the game you will not see a dialogue of characters (so there is no language limit for this game.) You need your own wisdom to escape this mysterious basement The end of the game is not unique There are 12 ordinary CGS and 3 hidden CGS in the game Come on. Friend! Hope you can escape from this evil space successfully!
